  "title": "93.2",
  "content": [
    {
      "type": "blockquote",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "As you rush down the streets, suddenly a reclaimer flies out of a\nnearby window and lands in a broken heap on the street in front of\nyou. You hear a bellowing voice shout \u201c\u2014and stay out!\u201d"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "You look in the window and see Elder Orlin standing in front of a\ngroup of frightened villagers. She spins a large hammer in slow circles,\nand as she does, the hammer\u2019s head begins to glow blue and hum. As\nyou start to call out to her, another reclaimer charges through a side\ndoor, and Elder Orlin pivots and swings. The hammer connects with\nthe reclaimer\u2019s chest with a flash of blue light and the tang of ozone.\nThen she turns and catches sight of you."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "\u201cWe\u2019ve got to get these people to safety!\u201d she says, swinging her\nhammer once again."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "em",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "p",
              "items": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Clear Elder Orlin with"
                },
                {
                  "type": "span",
                  "items": [
                    {
                      "type": "icon",
                      "icon": "progress"
                    }
                  ],
                  "icon_color": "black"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "to get her group out of the city."
                }
              ],
              "color": "blue"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "If you have"
        },
        {
          "type": "span",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "IMPRESSED ELDER ORLIN"
            }
          ],
          "color": "blue"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": ", add 2"
        },
        {
          "type": "span",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "icon",
              "icon": "progress"
            }
          ],
          "icon_color": "black"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "to her."
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
